==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zealant
<hw>Zeal"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is zealous; a
zealot; an enthusiast.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To certain <qex>zealants</qex>, all speech of pacification is
odious.</q> <rj><qau>Bacon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zealed</ent>⟦br⟧
